another random person. You give a gift to someone and you get a gift from
someone else.

You should get a gift for:

<%= @draw.receiver.name %>

<% if @draw.event.amount? and not @draw.event.amount.empty? %>
The suggested amount for the gift is: <%= @draw.event.amount %>.
<% end %>

